DrJamez

Let's make some words.

Rules: You cannot post twice in a row, someone must post before you.

Your word can either be 3 letters minimum or up to 5. (make use of the vowels and constants or just use straight up letters only)

You can only try to make three words in one post.

You get 1 point for a 3 letter word, 5 points for a 4 letter word, and 10 points for a 5 letter word.
Once you score, always post your score at the bottom of your post, so you can keep track and brag about the imaginary points you have.

Simple.

The person who makes the most words in this thread before we reach the post limit gets nothing. Absolutely nothing.

And how you can brag about that nothing won, people will find you a bother for days... Months if your a bagel.
